---
title: Apricot-Glazed Meatball Sandwich with Garlic Butter Rolls and Cranberry Salad
description: Sweet and tart, apricot spread adds a twist to our glazed meatballs! These meatballs are a dinner party classic. We've packed them into garlic butter buns to make an easy grab-and-go supper!
